  <brief_title>Comparison of Synchrony Between 4 NIV Ventilators</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Four Different Ventilators for Noninvasive Ventilation in Terms of Patient-ventilator Synchrony and Comfort</official_title>
  <sponsors>
