  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Comparison of the effects of 4 ventilators dedicated to NIV (2 home ventilators and 2
      ventilators designed for NIV) on patient-ventilator synchrony and comfort in patients
      admitted in the intensive care unit for respiratory failure and treated with NIV.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
